bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.filter

Interface BOperatorAccessors

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BDataAccessors
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BAccessorsBOutput

    public interface BOperatorAccessors
    This interface defines the operators available in a filterable data model. It aims at being the gateway between the filter engine and the filter UI.
    Author:
    Patrick G. Durand
